        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Growing up, I moved around the world, attending 14 different schools in 15 years. I was always an outlier, always questioning things, and often feeling like I saw solutions that others didn’t.</p><p>It was a bit lonely at times, but it taught me how to form deep connections quickly and how to dream big.</p><p>I always had ideas about products and solutions, and I’d often see those ideas come to life on store shelves years later. People even encouraged me to go on Shark Tank. But first, I had to fulfill my promise to my parents and get my degree.</p>",
